    <string name="privacy_policy_content">
        &lt;b&gt;Elder Desktop Privacy Policy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we handle your data.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;1. Data Collection:&lt;/b&gt; We do not collect or upload your personal information to any third-party servers. All settings and contacts are stored locally on your device.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;2. Permissions:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        - &lt;b&gt;Location:&lt;/b&gt; Used only to fetch weather data for your area.&lt;br/&gt;
        - &lt;b&gt;Contacts:&lt;/b&gt; Used to display speed dial shortcuts and import contact information.&lt;br/&gt;
        - &lt;b&gt;Notifications:&lt;/b&gt; Used to display your incoming messages on the desktop.&lt;br/&gt;
        - &lt;b&gt;Photos:&lt;/b&gt; Used only for setting contact profile pictures.&lt;br/&gt;
        - &lt;b&gt;Accessibility Service:&lt;/b&gt; Used strictly for \"Accidental Touch Prevention\" to block edge interactions. No data is collected or uploaded.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;3. No Advertisements:&lt;/b&gt; This app is strictly non-commercial and does not contain any advertising SDKs.&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &lt;b&gt;4. Open Source:&lt;/b&gt; You can verify our data handling logic by reviewing our source code on GitHub/GitLab.
    </string>
